==Useful Info==
'''Pharaoh ants''' are [[undead]] insects that roam the [[Spider's Nest]]. Upon death, they cast [[Bind Souls]] on all living creatures within line of sight.

==Tips & Tricks==
*The best way to deal with pharaoh ants is to kill them last. But they aren't non-threats outside of Bind Souls, with a fairly powerful [[drain]]ing melee attack.

==History==
* Pharaoh ants were added in [[0.28]].
